### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → ADMIN USERS — /api/v1/admin/admin-users
### ============================================================================

### List admin users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/admin-users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get admin user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/admin-users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create admin user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/admin-users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newadmin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!",
  "role": "SUPER_ADMIN"
}

### Update admin user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/admin-users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updatedadmin@example.com",
  "role": "SUPER_ADMIN"
}

### Delete admin user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/admin-users/{{adminUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
